OL,3,CSouth Tyneside Council proposes near
OL,4,C5% tax hike in bid to save #7m
OL,6,FPeople on are facing a 4.95% increase
OL,7,Fin their council tax as part of plans
OL,8,Fto balance the council's budget.
OL,10,FSouth Tyneside Council is planning the
OL,11,Fincrease alongside a raft of cost-
OL,12,Fcutting proposals to try and balance
OL,13,Fits budget.
OL,15,FThe local authority says it needs to
OL,16,Fsave #7m to balance its budget next
OL,17,Fyear, as well as using #8m from its
OL,18,Freserves.
