OL,3,CSouth Tyneside Council proposes near
OL,4,C5% tax hike in bid to save #7m
OL,6,FUnder the proposals, council services
OL,7,Fwould gain around #1.16 per week from
OL,8,Fa Band A property which the majority
OL,9,Fof homes on South Tyneside fall into.
OL,11,FThe increase would be a combination of
OL,12,Fthe Government's two per cent adult
OL,13,Fsocial care levy, which is ring-fenced
OL,14,Ffor those services, and a 2.95 per
OL,15,Fcent increase in council tax.
