OL,3,CSouth Tyneside Council proposes near
OL,4,C5% tax hike in bid to save #7m
OL,6,FNearly half of the council's savings
OL,7,Fwill come from adult social services
OL,8,Fand commissioning, along with plans to
OL,9,Fget rid of around 60 vacant council
OL,10,Fjob posts, reducing energy costs for
OL,11,Fthe council, and increasing car
OL,12,Fparking income.
OL,14,FIt is not the first time the council
OL,15,Fhas proposed increases, with funding
OL,16,Ffor local authority's having been cut
OL,17,Fover the last decade.
OL,19,FSince 2010 South Tyneside Council has
OL,20,Falready had to save #201 million.
