OL,3,CSouth Tyneside Council proposes near
OL,4,C5% tax hike in bid to save #7m
OL,6,FDespite pressures, council leaders are
OL,7,Fconfident they have plans in place to
OL,8,Fkeep key services going, making
OL,9,Fprogress on wider council priorities
OL,10,Fand protecting vulnerable residents.
OL,12,FCouncillor Joanne Bell, the council's
OL,13,Fcabinet member for governance, finance
OL,14,Fand corporate services, said it is
OL,15,Fincreasingly difficult to deliver the
OL,16,Flevel of savings needed.
