OL,6,FShe said: "Our services protect those
OL,7,Fin need and deliver essential services
OL,8,Fsuch as beach cleansing, street
OL,9,Flighting, , maintaining the roads and
OL,10,Fcleaning the streets.
OL,12,F"But we also provide support to older
OL,13,Fpeople, people with disabilities and
OL,14,Flooked after children in care.
OL,16,F"The cost of adults and children's
OL,17,Fsocial care accounts for 70 per cent
OL,18,Fof the council's discretionary budget
OL,19,Fso balancing the budget and protecting
OL,20,Fessential services is harder than ever
OL,21,Fbefore."
