OL,3,CSouth Tyneside Council proposes near
OL,4,C5% tax hike in bid to save #7m
OL,6,FThe council states it has made big
OL,7,Fchanges to the way it works in recent
OL,8,Fyears and has weighed up pressures
OL,9,Flike increased demand for services,
OL,10,Freduced central government funding,
OL,11,Fand competing commitments.
OL,13,FThough the budget for 2024/25 will be
OL,14,Fdecided at a meeting next month, there
OL,15,Fare some medium term plans to help
OL,16,Fwith planning, such as proposals to
OL,17,Fexpand the local provision of
OL,18,Fchildren's care homes and reduce
OL,19,Fcostly out-of-borough placements.
