OL,4,C5% tax hike in bid to save #7m
OL,6,FIt is also hoped lower-income families
OL,7,Fwill be supported through a revamped
OL,8,Fcouncil tax reduction scheme.
OL,10,FThe council says it will continue to
OL,11,Fsupport more than 10,000 working-age
OL,12,Fresidents who need help with their
OL,13,Fcouncil tax bills due to their
OL,14,Fpersonal circumstances.
