OL,3,CSouth Tyneside Council proposes near
OL,4,C5% tax hike in bid to save #7m
OL,6,FSouth Tyneside Council is also looking
OL,7,Fto make changes to bring it in line
OL,8,Fwith regional neighbours on home-to-
OL,9,Fschool transport and car parking, with
OL,10,Fcouncil parking charges set to rise in
OL,11,FSouth Shields town centre and the
OL,12,Fseafront.
OL,14,FSchool meal prices will also be frozen
OL,15,Ffor a fourth year, with South Tyneside
OL,16,FCouncil noting its record in providing
OL,17,F'the cheapest provision in the region'.
