OL,3,CSouth Tyneside Council proposes near
OL,4,C5% tax hike in bid to save #7m
OL,6,FDespite pressures put on the council's
OL,7,Fbudget it says that it is committed to
OL,8,Fhelping regenerate the area,
OL,9,Fincreasing investment and jobs.
OL,11,FThis includes improving council
OL,12,Fhousing, expanding Mortimer Community
OL,13,FCollege, upgrading the council's
OL,14,Fvehicle fleet, and continuing to
OL,15,Finvest in the International Advanced
OL,16,FManufacturing Park.
OL,18,FSouth Tyneside Council's cabinet will
OL,19,Fconsider the medium-term financial
OL,20,Fplan when it next meets on Wednesday
OL,21,F31 January.
